title: Love Where You Live! Townhome In Beautiful Garden Style Community!
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 875 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Nestled among the evergreens, our garden-style community is ideally located less than ten minutes from major employers such as Microsoft, Boeing and T-Mobile.', 'Offering studio, one, and two bedroom modern apartments for rent in Bellevue, WA, you’ll have no problem finding a home that you’ll love coming home to every day.', 'With the combination of contemporary interiors, relaxing community amenities, and an unbeatable location, what’s not to love about Edgewood Park Apartments?', 'Features:', 'Plank Floors*, Solid Surface Countertops*, Over-Sized Balcony or Patio*, Dishwasher, Walk-In Closets, Washer/Dryer Hook Ups, Balcony or Patio, Garbage Disposal, Broadband Internet Access, Extra Storage, Cable or Satellite, Fireplace*, Energy-Efficient, Stainless-Steel Appliances, Designer-Style Kitchen, Microwave*, 1-12 Month Leasing Options', '*In select apartment homes', 'Community Amenities:', 'Community Vegetable Garden, Emergency Maintenance, Bike Storage Room, WiFi in Lobby, On-Site Laundry Facilities, Near Public Transportation, Fitness Center, Package Receiving, Professional Management Team On-Site, Clubhouse, Two Sparkling Swimming Pools, Online Rental Payments, Pet Friendly, Dog Spa, Recycling Center', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats and dogs welcome, fees and restrictions apply.', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'Na9ljVhFLW']
